songs.title: Cadillac
songs.lyrics:
[Hook (x2)]
Holi holi chale Cadillac par lagge kinni tez chale
Kudiyan da dil dole vekh mainu
Mundeyan da dil jale

[Verse 1]
Holi holi chale meri Cadillac
Denali vangu sheeshe black
Tom Ford meri beat
Versace jiwe mera rap
Backseat 'ch karay beat bounce
Dashboard 'ch peya half ounce
Mainu G-Shock 'ch labheya ni
Kiwe Rolex 'ch mile time
Par same time hun Gametime
Heavyweight championship time
Hun KDM jiwe MGM
Sare rappers baithe ringside
Par sare rappers waste karan time
Main betha Westside te carefree
Hun main ladh da ni rappers nu ladunda jiwe referee
Par ajj kal de rappers to hunda main guess nahi
Te je main best nhi
Oh asli rappers da contest nhi
Ehde 'ch koi shaq nhi
Kihdi mere naal race lagge? Holi holi chaldi vi
Gaddi kinni tez lagge

[Hook (x2)]
Holi holi chale Cadillac par lagge kinni tez chale
Kudiyan da dil dole vekh mainu
Mundeyan da dil jale
Yeah

[Verse 2]
Par jado tez chale lagge slow
Jiwe road te bethe gaddi enni low (yeah)
Loki murh murh vekhde ni rajj de ve
Gaddi enni smooth jiwe chale bina clutch de ve
Main cruise karan par koi race la lai naal je
Tire burn hunde jiwe variyan de kalje
Nawa kehda aya jhine iss saal haarna ve
Mere to likhari nawe har saal haarde
Main jiwe shatranj kheda mere kol
10 jawaab ne variyan di har ik chaal de
Gaddi chale slow par kissi hor nu na de chance
Hun ode to vi slow meri Mercedes Benz
Main jiwe road te anokhi cheez aa gyi
Loki slow karan gaddi jiwe police aa gyi
Ve rap chad lokan ne produce kite song
Mere variyan ch jittan di umeed aa gyi
Par main KDM no. 1 jado da game 'ch
Gaddi meri kalli meri lane 'ch
Par main KDM no. 1 jado da game 'ch
Gaddi meri kalli meri lane 'ch

[Hook (x4)]
Holi holi chale Cadillac par lagge kinni tez chale
Kudiyan da dil dole vekh mainu
Mundeyan da dil jale

[Outro]
Mundeya da dil jale
Kudiyan da dil dole vekh mainu
Mundeya da dil jale....
Mundeya da dil jale....
Kudiyan da dil dole vekh mainu
Mundeya da dil jale....
Mundeya da dil jale....
